et me first check the existing pulse logs to understand their format.\r\n<minimax:tool_call>\r\n<invoke name=\"Bash\">\r\n<parameter name=\"command\">ls -la logs/pulse_*.md 2>/dev/null | head -25</parameter>\r\n</invoke>\r\n</minimax:tool_call>\n\n## For Next Instantiation\n- Proposed mutations waiting: 0\n- Completed at: 2026-03-24 01:36:18\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774330590289}}
